OL,3,CPolice chase caught on camera as
OL,4,Cdriver flees officers, crawling
OL,5,Cthrough gardens
OL,7,FWATCH: Dramatic bodycam footage shows
OL,8,FThames Valley Police officers pursuing
OL,9,Fand arresting 21-year-old Lewis
OL,10,FCollier.
OL,12,FBodycam footage shows a dramatic
OL,13,Fpolice chase through residential
OL,14,Fgardens in Reading after a driver
OL,15,Fmounted a pavement, smashed into a
OL,16,Froad sign, and tried to escape on foot.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
