OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784373493
OL,3,CPolice chase caught on camera as
OL,4,Cdriver flees officers, crawling
OL,5,Cthrough gardens
OL,7,FRealising he had been seen, Collier
OL,8,Freversed the vehicle, mounted a
OL,9,Fpavement, and collided with a
OL,10,Fstationary car before speeding away
OL,11,Ffrom the scene.
OL,13,FCollier then drove toward Southcote
OL,14,FLane, where he lost control of the
OL,15,FAudi and crashed directly into a
OL,16,FSulham Walk road sign.
OL,18,FWith his vehicle heavily damaged,
OL,19,FCollier decided to ditch the car and
OL,20,Fflee on foot.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
