PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784373493
OL,3,CPolice chase caught on camera as
OL,4,Cdriver flees officers, crawling
OL,5,Cthrough gardens
OL,7,FHe was filmed scaling residential
OL,8,Fgarden fences on Hatford Road in a
OL,9,Fdesperate bid to evade the pursuing
OL,10,Fofficers.
OL,12,FHis escape attempt came to an abrupt
OL,13,Fend moments later when officers caught
OL,14,Fup with him as he tried to crawl
OL,15,Fundetected through a nearby garden.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
