PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784373493
OL,3,CPolice chase caught on camera as
OL,4,Cdriver flees officers, crawling
OL,5,Cthrough gardens
OL,7,FFollowing the sentencing, a
OL,8,Fspokesperson for Thames Valley Police
OL,9,Fissued a stark warning to drug
OL,10,Foffenders in the area:"We will not
OL,11,Ftolerate drug-related offending in
OL,12,FReading. We will target and prosecute
OL,13,Foffenders and our activity will be
OL,14,Fboth visible and covert, aimed at
OL,15,Fdisrupting and pursuing offenders
OL,16,Finvolved in the supply of drugs."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
